Open Standard License — STILE Reference Implementation

STILE — Structural Integration Leverage (Delivery Without Communication)
Shunyaya Structural Resolution Model

Legal Status

This license is a permissive Open Standard license for the STILE reference implementation.

To the maximum extent permitted by applicable law, this license grants rights similar in spirit to permissive open-source licenses, while preserving truthful representation requirements for the STILE name and reference implementation.

If any provision is found unenforceable, the remaining provisions remain in effect.

Nature of Release

This is a minimal, self-contained reference implementation.

It is intended to demonstrate a structural delivery correctness model — not to represent a complete messaging system, communication protocol, or distributed delivery infrastructure.

Behavioral guarantees apply only within the scope of the reference model and its defined structural assumptions.

