Responsibility

Use of STILE in real-world systems is entirely at the user’s own responsibility.

This reference implementation provides:

• deterministic structural delivery resolution with reproducible delivery state and certificate
• delivery correctness from structure
• safe handling of incomplete and conflicting structure

It does not provide:

• message transport guarantees
• network reliability guarantees
• physical delivery guarantees
• system-level execution guarantees
• safety-critical assurances
• regulatory or compliance guarantees

