Closing Statement

STILE explores a simple but fundamental idea:

Delivery correctness emerges deterministically from structure, without communication, acknowledgements, retries, or network dependency.

Communication may reveal delivery.
It does not determine it.

It is released to encourage:

• independent validation
• real-world testing
• safe experimentation

STILE is offered as a minimal reference implementation of that possibility.
